== Xri xantadurga deusthan- nanoddem ==

gõychea nanoddem vattharant axil'lem mhotvachem deusthan. Hem deusthan mullchem bardesantlea kollongutt hea gamvant axil'lem. Punn purtugezanchea kallant 1577 vorsa battabatti vellar xri devi mohamaya kollonguttokorinn hika nanoddem gamvant haddli. Hem mull deusthan kollongutt hanga roinnichea rupant axil'lem. Hem deusthan udhvosth zaunche char dis adim deusthanacho mull puzari bhikubhott bhoskure haka sakxatkar zalo. Battabattik lagun ti hea gamvak vittlea ten'na ti sangta thoim tika vhor. Tinnem sangle te promann bhikubhott nanoddoya vochun sthanik zalo. Xri xantadurga mohamaya kollonguttokorinn hea doivtabhair hanga bara anuxangik doivtancho aspavo asa.

Xri xantadurga mohamaya hem mukhel doivt roinnichea rupant asa. Hea deullacho karbhar mohazon monddoll polleta. Hatunt ogsari naik, desai gadd, xettye, saunt, porob, naik hea so vangddeancho aspavo zata.Hea dexant xibikotsou, zagor, nouratr, dosro, kozagiri, xrilkxminarainnachi zatra, kalo, man'ni punou, xigmo, somvtsor protipoda, adi utsou ani deukriteam zatat.


== Xri xantadurga kumbharozumvekorinn-maxel ==

gõychea fonddem talukeantlea maxel vattharant axil'lem namnechem deusthan. Tika purvil'lea kallant hi santeri hea namvan vollkhotale. Punn sodea xri xantadurga kumbharozumvekorinn heach namvan tika vollkhotat. Tichem mull sthan khorli gamvchea madgade vaddear axil'lem. Pum' i.So. 1540 vorsa adim jen'na tisvaddi va gõy zumveavoili deullam purtogezamni udhvost korpak survat keli ten'na xri panddu naik voddie hea mullchea kumbharozumvechea monxan xri santeri devichi murt lipoun haddun aplea ghorchea devareant douroli.To zori kumbharozumve vattharant rautalo tori tacho vepar-dhondo madgade hanga xri santeri deulla lagsar axil'lo ani tachi devacher khor xrodhda axil'li. Fuddem battabattichea vellar prosongaudhan rakhun tannem kubharozumve hanga sthapon kel'lea xri santeri devichem sollavea xotmanantuch fonddem mhalachea vorgamv gamvant maxel vaddear stholantor kelem. Uprant hanga kubharozumvechea sogllea rohivaxamni mellun svokhrchan devull bandun tatunt xri santeri devichi protixtthapona keli.

Xri devi santeri- xri xantadurga kumbharozumvekorinn hi sogllea kumbharozumve gramvasiyanchi gram' deuta asun ticho soglleant vhodd ani mhotvacho utsou mhollear he devichi palkhi maxelantlean dor vorsam kumbharozumveam, aplea mull gamvant yeta ani thoinchea gramvasi hindu lokanchea ghorant mirounnukin thoinchea lokankoddlean puza orcha svikarota. Uprant porot aple suvater vota. Ho kall falgun mhoineache nimanne ani choitr mhoineache surveche dis somprokxonn vidhi zatkuch choitr xukl ponchmichea utsovacho karyokmr monoitat.

Xri kxetr maxel hanga mukhel deullant mukheasonar xri xantadurga kumbharozumvekorinn, gorbhokuddi bhair darache ujveutten eka choukant lingrupi xri grampurus,deullache ujveutten vegllea rodeullant xri roullonath, kumbharozumvem gamvant 'gamvant' namvachea vaddear ramaisoti namvan volkhupant yeupi don murti asat. Hea deullache dave votten lhanxa deullant 'gaddvoms'namvachem doivt asa. Him sogllim xri xantadrga kumbharozumvekorinn devichim sohporivar doivta asat.

Xri xantadurga devicho palkhi potsou va xibikotsou dor mhoineachea xukl 5 mi.Toxench vody 5 mi. Disa oxe don khepo neman zata. Te bhair her soglleo sonn porbo hea deullant monoitat.

